div.div:


                            Ex :


                            public abstract class A
                          
                          {
 private int id;
}

public class B extends A
                          {
...
}


                            If I omit id in serialization of class B like this :


                            xStream.omitField(B.class, "id");
                          

It doesn't work, XStream still serializes "id".
